public static void main(String args[])
{

}

public:-->
	=> public is a access modifier it will allow any
		public class information to call..
		
	=> Allow any public method or public variable to call

static:-->
	=> static is a access specifier. It will allow only
	   static methods to call without object creation.

void:-->
	=> Void is a method type it doesn't return value
		[other than void all methods return values]

main:-->
	=> main is a method name [Only main method will have this name]

String args[]:-->
	=> Parameters accept by main method in array format..
------------------------------------------------------------------------->>